== Tudert d uglam ==
[[Asirem n tudert]] n welɣem win yettilin gar n 30 ar 40 n iseggasen, [[Tiddi (tusnakt)|addud-is]] mara ad yili d ummid (kemmil) 1,85 m ar tuyat, d 2,15 m ar umeddis, Ameddis d win yeflalen (ɛlayen) s wazal n 75 cm ɣef [[tafekka|tfekka]], Ma d tizzli n welɣem d tin yettawaṭen ar 65 km deg tesragt

== Ismawen n welɣem s Tmaziɣt == 
